title: On-Site Management, Package Room, Underground Bicycle Parking
posting_body: ['3001 SE 4th St, Minneapolis, MN 55414', 'The Louis Apartments offers 70 homes and is located in the Prospect Park Neighborhood of Minneapolis.', 'Prospect Park is situated between the University of Minnesota to the west, St. Paul to the east, University Avenue to the north and the Mississippi River to the south.', 'The Louis is just north of University Avenue and It is a block away from the Metro Green Line Train - Prospect Park Station.', "Across the Street is Fresh Thyme Farmer's Market and is close by to many shops, restaurants, businesses and parks, including the historic Witch's Tower.", 'Ask us about our rent specials!!', 'Amenities Include:', 'Microwave', '99 Bike Score', 'Fitness Room', 'BBQ/Picnic Area', 'Package Room', 'Dishwasher', 'Bathtub', 'Underground Heated Garage', 'Underground Bicycle Parking', 'Computer Lab', 'Carpeting', 'Elevator', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'or email:thelouis at aeon dot org', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised apartment.', 'Please contact us today for the most updated information.', 'Professionally managed by Aeon, a provider of Fair housing and Equal Opportunity']
